This paper deals with the optimization of pre-trained neural networks, specifically in terms of weight discretization. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques and algorithms, which could fall under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
